<section class="mb-10">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 pb-2 border-b-2 border-gray-200">Technical Architecture</h2>

<div class="bg-gray-900 text-blue-300 p-5 rounded-lg font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre my-4">    User pastes doc numbers (any format)
                |
                v
        [Smart Input Parser]
        Split on: commas, spaces, OR, newlines
        Trim, deduplicate, validate
                |
                v
        [Load Saved Search]
        Script parameter: search ID
        Dynamic filter: tranid anyof [values]
                |
                v
        [Run Search + Render]
        Column headers from search metadata
        Results as professional HTML table
        Not-found numbers highlighted
                |
                v
        [Display to User]</div>

